reviewText:
AS MR COLLINS DRONE ON AND ON, I FELL ASLEEP AND WOKE TO
SEE HIM CRAWL AROUND EMPTY CHAMBERS FULL OF ROCKS AND
DIRT.  THE TITLE SHOULD HAVE BEEN "LECTURE AND SLIDE
PRESENTATION OF MY EXPLORATION OF UNDERGROUND EMPTY
CHAMBERS NEAR PYRAMID".
  SORRY TO SEE THE A.R.E. NAME ATTACHED TO THIS DVD BY
MR. COLLINS.
